snippet.title: Mario Bros: Lost World Trailer (SMBX2) - NFGD 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Demo here! (https://gamejolt.com/games/Mariolostworld/849745)

Mario and Luigi are working on the pipes when suddenly they find something off about one. The brothers both enter the pipe and are brought to this new world, something they've never seen before.

Watch the full presentation: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQR9NG65ONw
